{"tid":469154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴獲准推$800數碼月票 每日限搭10程車","createTime":"2017-11-15T04:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T05:43:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f02069b5b4ab9fbaa0f7da6b3485700cd3bb7e18","tid":469154,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:58:26.000Z","msg":"運輸署批准九巴推出數碼月票，售價約800元，適用於乘搭九巴大部份專營路線，每天限搭10程車。民建聯立法會議員劉國勳今日引述運輸署消息，指署方已就討論多時的九巴月票計劃「開綠燈」，待八達通公司解決技術問題後，市民即可使用九巴月票。他指月票包括所有九巴、聯營巴士和通宵巴士；而港鐵接駁巴士、口岸巴士、和假日馬場專線巴士等路線就每日限用兩次，避免濫用。<br />\n<br />\n劉國勳指，月票初步費用約800元，而日後政府實施《免入息審查的公共交通費用補貼計畫》後，市民有望在以每月700元使用月票，他期望在費用日後再有調整。而月票日後可在50個九巴的巴士總站買到月票。記者以每月22天工作、每天上下班乘巴士計算，用月票平均每程車費約18元，估計用月票乘長途巴士線相等於七五折優惠。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，九巴推出的數碼月票，會將購買者的資料轉移到他們的八達通卡上，無需另行持一張實體月票乘搭巴士，現正待八達通公司處完技術問題，就可確實計劃正式推出日期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171115/57460368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F57460368&d=wbblXAdUUDw7h6ZmuthJ0P%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=4f4269c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F57460368&h=24ff8d55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171115/57460368</a>"},{"pid":"c2e9b9404d48fe731daa0b3ca44d923a7822b438","tid":469154,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:59:51.000Z","msg":"當一個月返廿日工<br />\n<br />\n每日來回40 有賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e45430a74b96d1fb39ed5f05c65f457215e4638","tid":469154,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:02:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當一個月返廿日工<br />\n<br />\n每日來回40 有賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n奴隸表示返26日 出左必買"},{"pid":"26d9c92cf71cddb5217876644b94fa5b283ff025","tid":469154,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:03:50.000Z","msg":"係咪唔計龍運"},{"pid":"de27547b519ebe27c7331ef671a4c9ad0afd1b8b","tid":469154,"uid":67212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:05:02.000Z","msg":"聯營都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要唔要搭正九巴開既先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8129758b7757fe66cdbda413fd98a54437c5a0","tid":469154,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:09:06.000Z","msg":"巴膠福音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8e7986eea389f314a63a5cedf02898dee760ca","tid":469154,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:15:51.000Z","msg":"日日搭968  十分好"},{"pid":"420090326eeaa7d68b709d1478155866643646bd","tid":469154,"uid":46669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:23:07.000Z","msg":"睇黎應該無龍運份"},{"pid":"a39df6ac2f88b5df60cd04639dd20118910fad12","tid":469154,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:43:01.000Z","msg":"搭得龍運嘅都焗搭, 邊駛減<br />\n商家唔會死錯人"}]}